From: Graeme Smecher <gsmecher@t0.technology>
Date: Tue, 22 Jul 2025 13:48:14 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Workaround for pre-PEP 621 setuptools

The scarthgap setuptools is too old to understand PEP 639 license
expressions (license = "<SPDX identifier>"). Substitute the older
file-based form.
---
--- a/pyproject.toml
+++ b/pyproject.toml
@@ -20,7 +20,7 @@
     "Programming Language :: Python :: 3",
     "Operating System :: OS Independent",
 ]
-license = "BSD-3-Clause"
+license = {file="LICENSE"}
 dynamic = ["version", "scripts"]
 
 [project.optional-dependencies]
